author: Yoda____
title: Kabaya sweets?
review: I might as well just copy the review for the racing car but I can't be bothered so... I got this set free with a meal at legoland, to me it is charming and goes well with the car which is strange considering they are on a different scale. It is free so my standards are low but none the less it is charming so for me it gets a 5.
